name: Bedtime Stories
description:
Who could sleep with a collection of books like these? 50 Shades of who?

Printed on 50% supima cotton 50% micro modal available in Small, Medium and Large.

name: Uptown Girls
description:
It’s “a mod mod world.” A bevy of models in 60′s style clothes, hair and make-up strike poses in this Ivory colored crop tee.

Printed on 50% supima cotton 50% micro modal available in Small, Medium and Large.

name: Ladies Choice
description:
How cute is this tee? With so many lash styles to choose on this short sleeve tee, why pick one?

Printed on 50% supima cotton 50% micro modal available in Small, Medium and Large.

name: Hand of Fate
description:
Can you see your reflection.
This seasons version of our Logo tee.
A manicured hand holding a compact sitting on top of this black luxury v-neck.

name: Film Fatale
description:
A mysterious woman and an unknown symbol are the only clues you’ll find on this vintage pink bib  style tee with open back cut out.

Printed on 50% supima cotton 50% micro modal available in Small, Medium and Large

name: Icon Tee
description:
A shout out to our favorite style icons of cinema and song.
If you have to ask then….

Printed on 100% cotton available in Small, Medium and Large.

name: Premonition Tank
description:
Super Soft and Drapey! This print is a composite of the four heads
used in the Intuition art series.

It's printed in filmy blue that captures the dreamy quality of this print perfectly. 

Printed on the softest organic cotton ever!

name: Mediation Crop
description:
This awesome tank with the long arm holes was a big seller at Unique LA and Renegade this December.

The print is the Tminx's symbolic wink to re-using and re-cycling
with out the message being over the top.

name: Clairvoyance Tank
description:
Part of the Intuition Series this tank is so slinky and soft you'll never stop wearing it. It has a dreamy other worldly vibe. The print is water based and sits inside the shirt ever so gently. 

Great under a blazer, or alone if you dare.

name: Second Sight Short Sleeve T-shirt
description:
This was a graphic from a vintage panty hose package found at thrift store in Baldwin Park back in the early 00's. I knew I would eventually photoshop flip it for something, and well her time finally came.

Water based Ink, available in Small, Medium, and Large and printed on the finest organic cotton.

name: Birds
description:
Interiors
Inspired by the interiors of the 60’s and 70’s.  Elements from wallpaper swatches have been deconstructed and re-interpreted on a muted palette of black, white, grey and beige giving these designs a contemporary look.

“Blue Birds”
These decorative birds perched and gathered in and on the cage manage to be sophisticated and mysterious all at once.

Printed on the back of soft white fabric imbues this shirt with a low-key feel. 100% Rayon. One Size.

Printed on the front of the softest slate grey fabric and the shirt takes on a modern and chic appeal. 100% Rayon. One Size.

name: Art Deco
description:
Interiors
Inspired by the interiors of the 60’s and 70’s. Elements from wallpaper swatches have been deconstructed and re-interpreted on a muted palette of black, white, grey and beige giving these designs a contemporary look.

“Art Deco”
Clean, bold graphic lines characterize this print. An homage to the Art Deco revival popular in the early 1970’s.

Printed on the softest 100% Rayon. One Size.

name: House
description:
Interiors
Inspired by the interiors of the 60’s and 70’s. Elements from wallpaper swatches have been deconstructed and re-interpreted on a muted palette of black, white, grey and beige giving these designs a contemporary look.

“House on Hill”
One of my favorite of the bunch, this artful image of a warm abode is composed mostly of ivory colored dots. The house is placed on the back of the tank, You’ll feel extra special knowing your wearing something unexpected.

Printed on the softest 100% Rayon. Small, Medium, Large.

name: Lace
description:
Interiors
Inspired by the interiors of the 60’s and 70’s. Elements from wallpaper swatches have been deconstructed and re-interpreted on a muted palette of black, white, grey and beige giving these designs a contemporary look.

“Lace Tank”
This slinky tank is inspired by the boudoirs of the 1960’s. The lace motif has been rearranged and placed straight down the back of this tank, giving it the perfect accent.

Printed on the softest 100% Rayon. Small, Medium, Large.

name: Art Deco Swirl
description:
Interiors
Inspired by the interiors of the 60’s and 70’s. Elements from wallpaper swatches have been deconstructed and re-interpreted on a muted palette of black, white, grey and beige giving these designs a contemporary look.

“Art Deco Swirl”
This image is streamlined down to the most basic design elements.
All that’s left are remnants of a large swirl. The muted grey against black gives this design an understated vibe.

Printed on the softest 100% Rayon. One Size.

name: Boxes de Perfume
description:
Pillow Talk
The essence of Pillow Talk is an array of imagery meant to convey all the soft caresses and sweet nothings lovers whisper into each others ears.

Boxes de Perfume
The counterpoint to the Bottles of Perfume is the Boxes de Perfume. Reminding you of your favorite perfumes that you loved so much you wouldn’t dare discard the box. Stacked and arranged as they would be in your cabinet reminding you of all the nights of magic they brought.

Printed on 50% Cotton/50% Modal available in Small, Medium & Large.

name: Gold Story
description:
Pillow Talk
The essence of Pillow Talk is an array of imagery meant to convey all the soft caresses and sweet nothings lovers whisper into each others ears.

The Gold Story
A hint of gold tells the story of the teddy bear, the owl, the snail, the lamp and many others. Each glowing in it’s own spectacular way. For the shirt the print has been turned white and set upon on the softest black tee imaginable.

Printed on 100% Rayon. Available in Small, Medium & Large.

name: Perfume
description:
Pillow Talk
The essence of Pillow Talk is an array of imagery meant to convey all the soft caresses and sweet nothings lovers whisper into each others ears.

Bottles of Perfume
Nothing evokes more fantasy and romance than perfume. Beautiful vintage perfume bottles have been lovingly displayed as if they were on your vanity, each awaiting their turn for a night on the town.

Printed on 50% Cotton/50% Modal available in Small, Medium & Large.

name: High Society Print
description:
Red ink against the softest rayon available.
Short sleeve Crop tee shirt.

name: What's Your Sign-Tminx Zodiac Baseball Tee
Fitted and Flattered 20 x 30 Print
description:
Part of the colorful geometric series. These fashion croqui's take their 
cue from vintage sewing pattern packages. They've been sketched by 
free hand then cleaned up and colorized with the computer.
Hope you like it.

The prints are unmounted and rolled and  shipped in a poster tube with confirmation delivery.
